      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I see that. It's still a bit intimidating to think about being personally liable for huge legal costs. Are there any other \"hidden\" things in these kinds of clauses I should look out for? Like, are there ways these clauses can be sneaky or catch people off guard?",
